column2: Watch Donald Trump become the 45th President of the United States.
Earlier today a reporter shouted to Obama, "Any last words for the American people?" He just replied, "Thank you."
Mike Pence has just been sworn in. Now officially US Vice President.
All the living former presidents, except George H W Bush, who is in hospital are present for the inauguration.
This music is by the Missouri State University Chorale
Sitting on the podium, Hillary Clinton, the woman who wanted to become 45th President of the United States
